Hi all! We've been relying on the SQL database more and more for recent projects. Currently, we have a lot of projects in-flight that use new database tables, so I summarized everything here: Database Schema Changes Index (https://docs.google.com/document/d/12V346LHpa1sSQby0FEr_ooCCeoN2xXbf8wjvA2KdNc0/edit). Take a look if you're interested in seeing what kinds of projects teams are using the database for! If anything is missing or incorrect, feel free to edit.

cc @lydia @Eric Han @andy @Heymian @shaunak
